{
  "stem": "18102.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so one has to be a little skeptical about the-- this ability of changing human nature and making people speak out in anger when they see an atrocity of this sort.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My hope is, though, that we can change.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And education is the only way that, perhaps, will cause that change.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have to, as Jews, be more mindful, and we are, of these events and be the teachers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe we were the chosen people for many reasons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But certainly, the reason of teaching, and of memory, and of bringing out the best in the world is our mission, at least I feel that way.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think the story of Sugihara is one direct method of showing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Here's a-- what he did, how he stood up, how he was dictated by his conscience, and what was the result?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, look at the result of the lives saved.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know the saying about saving one life saves the entire generation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He has done that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think we can show, in vivid form, what, what the value of such a courage and such a humanitarianism means.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think we have to show that in conjunction with what happened to those that weren't fortunate enough to fall in, in a way-- I mean to find themselves in, in a way that they could be saved by a Sugihara, because most of the millions weren't that lucky, as I was.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we have to show their story, and we have to use that as an antithesis-- the, the black and white, as it were, of when a human being intervenes to save the lives, versus when the rest of the world does not intervene and allows the atrocity.",
      "word_count": 49
    }
  ],
